                    FP(I) = DummyNumS - SommaS: VN(I) = SommaS
                    Sens(I) = VP(I) / (VP(I) + FN(I))
                    Spec(I) = VN(I) / (VN(I) + FP(I))
                        If VP(I) + FP(I) <> 0 Then
